ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course is very suitable for the students who are going to pursue mathematics related research. Of course, it is still useful for the students who love programming of applied mathematics. Thus, I will be recommending the course to the students who satisfy the above conditions.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I am always interested in math. The professor taught me a lot.

Because there are some programming assignments in this course, I could exercise my programming ability during taking the course, and I could also learn some interesting skills related to applied mathematics from the course.
